  "title": "Server side rendering: being able to trigger the search server side",
  "body": "Feature request\r\n\r\n**What is the current behavior?**\r\n\r\nCurrently when rendering a react-instantsearch page with [next](https://zeit.co/blog/next) it doesn't send a page with results already fetched from Algolia.\r\n\r\n**What is the expected behavior?**\r\n\r\nIt would be great if this could be achieved without any configuration. Otherwise, it would be enough to provide a guide that explains how to do it (and change the API or the internals to make it possible, if needed).",
